{
  "page": "Black Lorren",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><table class=\"infobox\" style=\"min-width:22em;max-width:32em;border-collapse:separate;border-spacing:3px\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;font-size:125%;font-weight:bold;font-weight:bold; background: none; line-height: 1.1em;\">Black Lorren</th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" class=\"infobox-image\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n<a href=\"/index.php/File:Black_Lorren_TheMico.jpg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Black Lorren TheMico.jpg\" src=\"/images/thumb/f/fb/Black_Lorren_TheMico.jpg/350px-Black_Lorren_TheMico.jpg\" width=\"350\" height=\"495\" srcset=\"/images/f/fb/Black_Lorren_TheMico.jpg 1.5x\" /></a><div>Art by TheMico</div></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n<hr /></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Alias</th><td>\nBlack Lorren</td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Title</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Castellan\" title=\"Castellan\">Castellan</a> of <a href=\"/index.php/Winterfell\" title=\"Winterfell\">Winterfell</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Allegiance</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/House_Greyjoy\" title=\"House Greyjoy\">House Greyjoy</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Culture</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Ironborn\" title=\"Ironborn\">Ironborn</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Died</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/299_AC\" title=\"299 AC\">299&#160;AC</a><br /><a href=\"/index.php/Sack_of_Winterfell\" title=\"Sack of Winterfell\">Winterfell</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Book</th><td>\n<i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Clash_of_Kings\" title=\"A Clash of Kings\">A Clash of Kings</a></i> (appears)</td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n<hr /></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\"><span style=\"white-space:nowrap\">Played by</span></th><td>\nForbes KB</td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\"><span style=\"white-space:nowrap\">TV series</span></th><td>\n<i><a href=\"/index.php/Game_of_Thrones\" title=\"Game of Thrones\">Game of Thrones</a></i>: <a href=\"/index.php/Game_of_Thrones_-_Season_2\" title=\"Game of Thrones - Season 2\">Season 2</a></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p><b>Black Lorren</b> is a famous <a href=\"/index.php/Ironborn\" title=\"Ironborn\">ironborn</a> fighter.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Racok37.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Racok37.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>In the television adaptation <i><a href=\"/index.php/Game_of_Thrones\" title=\"Game of Thrones\">Game of Thrones</a></i>, Lorren is portrayed by Forbes KB.\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Appearance_and_Character\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Appearance and Character</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#Recent_Events\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Recent Events</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#A_Clash_of_Kings\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\"><i>A Clash of Kings</i></span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#Quote_by_Lorren\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Quote by Lorren</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#Quotes_about_Lorren\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Quotes about Lorren</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-6\"><a href=\"#External_Links\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">5</span> <span class=\"toctext\">External Links</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-7\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">6</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Appearance_and_Character\">Appearance and Character</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Black_Lorren&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Appearance and Character\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<dl><dd><i>See also: <a href=\"/index.php/Category:Images_of_Black_Lorren\" title=\"Category:Images of Black Lorren\">Images of Black Lorren</a></i></dd></dl>\n<p>Lorren is a squat, thick man with a long black beard.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Racok46.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Racok46.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup> He wields axe and sword.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Racok66.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Racok66.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>Black Lorren and <a href=\"/index.php/Qarl_the_Maid\" title=\"Qarl the Maid\">Qarl the Maid</a> are considered among the fiercest <a href=\"/index.php/Ironborn\" title=\"Ironborn\">ironborn</a> warriors, behind only <a href=\"/index.php/Andrik_the_Unsmiling\" title=\"Andrik the Unsmiling\">Andrik the Unsmiling</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Racok37.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Racok37.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup> Lorren is willing to die in battle and is contemptuous of underhanded tactics.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Racok66.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Racok66.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Recent_Events\">Recent Events</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Black_Lorren&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Recent Events\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"A_Clash_of_Kings\"><i>A Clash of Kings</i></span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Black_Lorren&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: A Clash of Kings\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<p>Black Lorren is among the <a href=\"/index.php/Ironborn\" title=\"Ironborn\">ironborn</a> who participate in the <a href=\"/index.php/Harrying_of_the_Stony_Shore\" title=\"Harrying of the Stony Shore\">harrying of the Stony Shore</a>, during which he and <a href=\"/index.php/Urzen\" title=\"Urzen\">Urzen</a> silence animals too badly wounded to be saved. <sup id=\"cite_ref-Racok37.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Racok37.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup> \n</p><p>Lorren is part of <a href=\"/index.php/Theon_Greyjoy\" title=\"Theon Greyjoy\">Theon Greyjoy</a>'s force that <a href=\"/index.php/Capture_of_Winterfell\" title=\"Capture of Winterfell\">captures Winterfell</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Racok46.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Racok46.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup> When Theon notices that <a href=\"/index.php/Summer\" title=\"Summer\">Summer</a> and <a href=\"/index.php/Shaggydog\" title=\"Shaggydog\">Shaggydog</a> have gone missing, he tasks Lorren with making a round of the castle's gates. Lorren finds <a href=\"/index.php/Drennan\" title=\"Drennan\">Drennan</a>'s body by the <a href=\"/index.php/Hunter%27s_Gate\" title=\"Hunter&#39;s Gate\">Hunter's Gate</a>, and Theon has him pull <a href=\"/index.php/Squint\" title=\"Squint\">Squint</a>'s body from the moat with a pike.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Racok50.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_4-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Racok50.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup> Theon leaves Lorren as his castellan when he searches for <a href=\"/index.php/Bran_Stark\" title=\"Bran Stark\">Bran</a> and <a href=\"/index.php/Rickon_Stark\" title=\"Rickon Stark\">Rickon Stark</a> in the <a href=\"/index.php/Wolfswood\" title=\"Wolfswood\">wolfswood</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Racok50.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_4-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Racok50.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>When <a href=\"/index.php/Asha_Greyjoy\" title=\"Asha Greyjoy\">Asha Greyjoy</a> arrives from <a href=\"/index.php/Deepwood_Motte\" title=\"Deepwood Motte\">Deepwood Motte</a>, Black Lorren brings her to the <a href=\"/index.php/Great_Hall_of_Winterfell\" title=\"Great Hall of Winterfell\">Great Hall of Winterfell</a> for breakfast. He and Asha both believe that Theon should abandon Winterfell, but Theon refuses their advice.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Racok56.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_5-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Racok56.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-5\">&#91;5&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>When <a href=\"/index.php/Northmen\" title=\"Northmen\">northmen</a> led by Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Rodrik_Cassel\" title=\"Rodrik Cassel\">Rodrik Cassel</a> arrive to retake Winterfell, Theon gathers the ironmen and offers them the choice of departing or staying to fight by his side. <a href=\"/index.php/Wex_Pyke\" title=\"Wex Pyke\">Wex Pyke</a>, Theon's squire, is the first to step forward in reponse, and Black Lorren follows next, shamed and scowling. Lorren advises Theon to expel the smallfolk of Winterfell to prevent them from attacking the remaining defenders, but Theon refuses. Lorren offers to defend Winterfell's drawbridge against attacking northmen by himself, but he is again refused. Instead, Theon chooses to stay Rodrik's attack by threatening to have Lorren hang his daughter, <a href=\"/index.php/Beth_Cassel\" title=\"Beth Cassel\">Beth Cassel</a>, during a parley; a disapproving Lorren views Theon with contempt.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Racok66.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Racok66.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>Black Lorren and Theon watch the <a href=\"/index.php/Battle_outside_the_gates_of_Winterfell\" title=\"Battle outside the gates of Winterfell\">battle outside the gates of Winterfell</a> from the castle's battlements. Lorren mans the main gate when \"Red Helm\" has the bodies of Rodrik, <a href=\"/index.php/Leobald_Tallhart\" title=\"Leobald Tallhart\">Leobald Tallhart</a>, and <a href=\"/index.php/Cley_Cerwyn\" title=\"Cley Cerwyn\">Cley Cerwyn</a> brought forward by men of the <a href=\"/index.php/Dreadfort\" title=\"Dreadfort\">Dreadfort</a>. Lorren, Theon, and Maester <a href=\"/index.php/Luwin\" title=\"Luwin\">Luwin</a> meet the victors in the yard, where \"Red Helm\" reveals himself to be <a href=\"/index.php/Ramsay_Snow\" title=\"Ramsay Snow\">Ramsay Snow</a>. Lorren defends himself with his sword when four men from <a href=\"/index.php/House_Bolton\" title=\"House Bolton\">House Bolton</a> attack him.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Racok66.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Racok66.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>After the <a href=\"/index.php/Sack_of_Winterfell\" title=\"Sack of Winterfell\">sack of Winterfell</a> by the Boltons, Bran Stark and his companions emerge from hiding in <a href=\"/index.php/Crypt_of_Winterfell\" title=\"Crypt of Winterfell\">the crypt</a>. They find Black Lorren's body in the yard, and <a href=\"/index.php/Osha\" title=\"Osha\">Osha</a> notices that he had been able to kill a few attackers before being slain.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Racok69.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_6-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Racok69.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-6\">&#91;6&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Quote_by_Lorren\">Quote by Lorren</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Black_Lorren&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Quote by Lorren\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<blockquote class=\"templatequote\" style=\"border-left:none;\"><div class=\"templatequotetext\"><p><b>Lorren</b>: <a href=\"/index.php/Ironborn\" title=\"Ironborn\">They</a> fear no foe in open battle, but it is another thing to dwell among enemies, never knowing if the washerwoman means to kiss you or kill you, or whether the serving boy is filling your cup with <a href=\"/index.php/Ale\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Ale\">ale</a> or bale. We would do well to leave this place.<br />\n<b>Theon</b>: I am the <a href=\"/index.php/Prince_of_Winterfell\" title=\"Prince of Winterfell\">Prince of Winterfell</a>! This is my seat, no man will drive me from it. No, <a href=\"/index.php/Asha_Greyjoy\" title=\"Asha Greyjoy\">nor woman</a> either!<sup id=\"cite_ref-Racok56.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_5-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Racok56.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-5\">&#91;5&#93;</a></sup></p></div><div class=\"templatequotecite\"><cite>&#8212;Lorren and <a href=\"/index.php/Theon_Greyjoy\" title=\"Theon Greyjoy\">Theon Greyjoy</a></cite></div>\n</blockquote>\n<blockquote class=\"templatequote\" style=\"border-left:none;\"><div class=\"templatequotetext\"><p>I'll take my axe and stand on that drawbridge, and let them come try me. One at a time, two, three, it makes no matter. None will pass the moat while I still draw breath.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Racok66.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-4\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Racok66.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup></p></div><div class=\"templatequotecite\"><cite>&#8212;Lorren to <a href=\"/index.php/Theon_Greyjoy\" title=\"Theon Greyjoy\">Theon Greyjoy</a></cite></div>\n</blockquote>\n<blockquote class=\"templatequote\" style=\"border-left:none;\"><div class=\"templatequotetext\"><p><b>Lorren</b>: Only blood can wash out blood. <a href=\"/index.php/Knight\" title=\"Knight\">Knights</a> may keep their truces with other knights, but they are not so careful of their honor when dealing with those they deem <a href=\"/index.php/Outlaw\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Outlaw\">outlaw</a>.<br />\n<b>Theon</b>: I am the <a href=\"/index.php/Prince_of_Winterfell\" title=\"Prince of Winterfell\">Prince of Winterfell</a> and heir to the <a href=\"/index.php/Iron_Islands\" title=\"Iron Islands\">Iron Islands</a>. Now go find <a href=\"/index.php/Beth_Cassel\" title=\"Beth Cassel\">the girl</a> and do as I told you.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Racok66.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-5\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Racok66.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup></p></div><div class=\"templatequotecite\"><cite>&#8212;Lorren and <a href=\"/index.php/Theon_Greyjoy\" title=\"Theon Greyjoy\">Theon Greyjoy</a></cite></div>\n</blockquote>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Quotes_about_Lorren\">Quotes about Lorren</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Black_Lorren&amp;action=edit&amp;section=5\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Quotes about Lorren\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<blockquote class=\"templatequote\" style=\"border-left:none;\"><div class=\"templatequotetext\"><p>The singers call <a href=\"/index.php/Andrik_the_Unsmiling\" title=\"Andrik the Unsmiling\">Andrik</a> best now. Andrik the Unsmiling, they name him. A giant of a man. He serves <a href=\"/index.php/Dunstan_Drumm\" title=\"Dunstan Drumm\">Lord Drumm</a> of <a href=\"/index.php/Old_Wyk\" title=\"Old Wyk\">Old Wyk</a>. And Black Lorren and <a href=\"/index.php/Qarl_the_Maid\" title=\"Qarl the Maid\">Qarl the Maid</a> are near as dread.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Racok37.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Racok37.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></p></div><div class=\"templatequotecite\"><cite>&#8212;<a href=\"/index.php/Dagmer_Cleftjaw\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Dagmer Cleftjaw\">Dagmer Cleftjaw</a> to <a href=\"/index.php/Theon_Greyjoy\" title=\"Theon Greyjoy\">Theon Greyjoy</a></cite></div>\n</blockquote>\n<blockquote class=\"templatequote\" style=\"border-left:none;\"><div class=\"templatequotetext\"><p><a href=\"/index.php/Winterfell\" title=\"Winterfell\">Winterfell</a> is yours in my absence. If we do not return, do with it as you will.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Racok50.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_4-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Racok50.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup></p></div><div class=\"templatequotecite\"><cite>&#8212;<a href=\"/index.php/Theon_Greyjoy\" title=\"Theon Greyjoy\">Theon Greyjoy</a> to Lorren</cite></div>\n</blockquote>\n<blockquote class=\"templatequote\" style=\"border-left:none;\"><div class=\"templatequotetext\"><p>He means to die, thought Theon. It's not victory he wants, it's an end worthy of a song.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Racok66.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-6\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Racok66.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup></p></div><div class=\"templatequotecite\"><cite>&#8212;thoughts of <a href=\"/index.php/Theon_Greyjoy\" title=\"Theon Greyjoy\">Theon Greyjoy</a></cite></div>\n</blockquote>\n<blockquote class=\"templatequote\" style=\"border-left:none;\"><div class=\"templatequotetext\"><p>He had been hacked and cut so badly that his beard looked a reddish-brown now.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Racok69.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_6-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Racok69.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-6\">&#91;6&#93;</a></sup></p></div><div class=\"templatequotecite\"><cite>&#8212;thoughts of <a href=\"/index.php/Bran_Stark\" title=\"Bran Stark\">Bran Stark</a></cite></div>\n</blockquote>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"External_Links\">External Links</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Black_Lorren&amp;action=edit&amp;section=6\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: External Links\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://gameofthrones.wikia.com/wiki/Lorren\">Lorren</a> on the <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://gameofthrones.wikia.com/wiki/Main\">Game of Thrones wiki</a>.</li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Black_Lorren&amp;action=edit&amp;section=7\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\" style=\"-webkit-column-width:200px; -moz-column-width:200px; column-width:200px; -webkit-column-count:2; -moz-column-count:2; column-count:2;\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Racok37.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Racok37.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">1.0</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Racok37.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D